      "html": "<p>Дана схема превращений:</p>"
    },
    {
      "html": "<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1.1rem; margin: 16px 0\">\n          Fe(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>\n          <span style=\"margin: 0 6px\">→</span>\n          Fe(OH)<sub>2</sub>\n          <span style=\"margin: 0 6px\">→</span>\n          X\n          <span style=\"margin: 0 6px\">→</span>\n          Fe<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub>\n        </p>"
