  "solution": {
    "title": "Эталон ответа (демоверсия ОГЭ 2025)",
    "html": "<ol style=\"margin-top: 12px; line-height: 1.7\">\n            <li>\n              Fe(NO<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub> + 2NaOH = Fe(OH)<sub>2</sub> +\n              2NaNO<sub>3</sub>\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              4Fe(OH)<sub>2</sub> + 2H<sub>2</sub>O + O<sub>2</sub> =\n              4Fe(OH)<sub>3</sub>\n              &nbsp;(X — Fe(OH)<sub>3</sub>)\n            </li>\n            <li>\n              2Fe(OH)<sub>3</sub> <span style=\"margin-left: 4px\">→</span\n              ><sup>t°</sup> Fe<sub>2</sub>O<sub>3</sub> + 3H<sub>2</sub>O\n            </li>\n          </ol>"
  }
